body: Now is the time to own the beach getaway that you've always dreamed of. This 4-bedroom 3 bath raised beach house is truly luxurious. Some of the features are fiber cement siding, stacked front porches that have beautiful views of the marsh and ocean, 10 ft ceilings on the main floor with nice crown and base board moldings, 42-inch kitchen cabinets with under cabinet lighting and crown, and a very open concept. Come and see this beautiful home for yourself and take advantage of all that Litchfield Beach has to offer. You'll be minutes away from the famous Marshwalk in Murrells Inlet, Huntington Beach State Park, several very nice golf courses, the attractions of Myrtle Beach, and a day trip to Charleston. Don't miss this opportunity!

body: Beautiful New Construction home in a lovely Montague Lakes. Montague Lakes offers a wonderful combination of amenities including a community pool, clubhouse, park areas and more. Great Southern Homes, one of the top builders in the state, has created a beautiful selection of floorplans and features that are sure to please. These homes are built with the utmost care and quality with an emphasis on producing a home that is not only pleasing to the eye, but also considerate of the environment. Some of the features this selection of homes will offer include brick skirting, fireplaces, top quality trim package, hardwood floors throughout the foyer, living, and dining areas, covered or screened porches(depending upon plan), and tile backsplashes. title: 524 Bella Woods Tr. (lot 6)
marketing_tagline: Our most popular plan with a half acre lot!
body:
Need some space to enjoy life? How about a five bedroom home on a half acre lot? Then check out Bella Woods and Great Southern Homes’ Bentcreek. It is a 5 bedroom, 3 full bath house with an attached 2 car garage on a half-acre lot. And if half an acre isn’t enough, we have one and two acre lots on which to build your home. Did we mention the lots are large? The fifth bedroom and a full bath are on first level your new home. And with its open floor plan concept, the chef will never be isolated in the kitchen. The kitchen includes maple cabinetry, recessed lights, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances. The master suite, secondary bedrooms, laundry and large open loft completes the home on the second level. This neighborhood is brought to you by Great Southern Homes, a Nationally ranked top 100 builder and one of the fastest growing builders in SC AND the Upstate. Awarded by the Home Builders Association of Greenville the "Green Builder Award in 2018! We also feature the Honeywell Home Automation smart home system as a standard feature! Truly a "Green & Smart" home builder, which allows you to control energy costs and home security remotely! As well as our Smartphone Docking system with speakers allowing you to enjoy your personal playlists! Bella Woods is located in the highly sought-after District 2 school system. With half-acre lots (or larger) you can enjoy life!
Move in Ready! Peaceful living with all of the convenience!
Call to schedule your personal tour of this and our other available homes in Bella Woods today!

NEW CONSTRUCTION!!! 5 BRs/3BAs + loft open-concept home in the desirable Fountainbrook community. The Bentgrass is an efficient plan that invites you to come in from the moment you drive up and see the craftsman-style exterior that says“Welcome home!” 6" luxury vinyl plank flooring meets you at the front door and beckons you to explore all that this popular split layout floor plan offers. The kitchen is a chef's delight and includes an island, 36” staggered maple cabinetry, recessed lights, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The spacious master suite includes a trey ceiling, dual sinks with granite vanity tops, a separate garden tub and shower, and a 2 walk-in-closets. This home also includes brushed nickel light fixtures, two tone paint, and extensive closet space throughout. Interested in a GreenSmart home? Live Green. Live Smart. This home includes a smart phone docking system connected to two built-in speakers, Honeywell's newly released Lyric™ home automation system, tankless hot water heater, radiant barrier roof sheathing. Fountainbrook qualifies for 100% USDA financing and is just a 5 minute drive to grocery/drug stores, restaurants, urgent care facilities, shopping, dining, and the IMAX movie theatre. Quick and easy access to I-385 makes Downtown Greenville, GSP airport, the mountains, nearby lakes, and SC, NC, & GA beaches just a short drive away.

To see a virtual tour of the Bentgrass model home please click here: https://vimeo.com/271668927
school(s): Fountain Inn Elementary,Bryson Middle School,Hillcrest High School

title: 1835 Wood Stork Drive
marketing_tagline: Live Your Dream in Wild Wing Plantation!
body:
There is ALOT of anti-claustrophobic EXTRA SPACE in this 4 bedroom, 3 ½ bath Aberdeen floor plan. Oversized foyer, dining and powder room (and master closet), and an incredible walk-up storage space upstairs, makes this Aberdeen a dream-home for all of us with too many kids, or too many Christmas decorations, or too many visiting relatives. With 2 bedrooms and 2 baths down, plans 2 bedrooms up AND the walk-up spacing whether finished or unfinished, everyone feels good about having their own spaces. 

UNDER CONSTRUCTION AND 60 DAYS FROM COMPLETION – 4 bedrooms, 3 ½ baths, and over 3200 total square feet. High-end finishes in a high-end neighborhood at Wild Wing Golf Plantation…without the high-end price! One a peaceful, quiet fishing pond known for putting a bass on the end of your line.

An award-winning South Carolina builder with a life long local legend of a superintendent at Wild Wing. Great Southern Homes is bringing you classic homes of quality and added space without the high price. This is NOT your typical cookie-cutter house!

title: 37 Donemere Way
marketing_tagline: The Model Home in Tucker Branch!!
Incentive: Great Southern Homes is having an End of the Summer Blowout Sale! Prices are Drastically Reduced on limited number of model homes! Plus, this is our last home available for sale in the exceptional Tucker Branch community! This opportunity will not last long! Act now to get your piece of paradise!
body:
This lovely model home is the very popular McClean plan with the optional Sun room. This open & inviting 4 bed/2.5 bath smart home has many upgrades starting with the 5" hand scraped hardwood floors throughout the entire lower level. The spacious foyer includes the coat closet and large powder room near the front door. The kitchen features a very large center island with double SS sink and Moen sprayer faucet. 36" staggered height maple cabinetry, recessed lights, granite counters and stainless steel appliances. The optional appliances (fridge, W/D) will also transfer with this home.The kitchen is open and adjacent to the family room (with a gas fireplace) and the sun room, making it perfect for entertaining family & friends. The mudroom, leading to the two car garage has a wall organizer for dropping backpacks, hanging jackets, etc. It also features a granite topped "desk" with two cabinets on the wall above. The 4 bedrooms are upstairs. All but one have walk-in closets and the master suite has two walk-in closets! The master bath has a large tiled shower, separate garden tub, dual sinks in granite vanity top and a framed mirror above the sinks. The second bath also has dual sinks in granite vanity top and a transom window for great natural lighting. The large laundry room is convienently located on 2nd level, so no hauling laundry up & down the stairs.

Tucker Branch qualifies for 100% financing USDA & other rural loan programs. The home is 1/2 mile from downtown Fountain Inn, yet is situated in Laurens County with it's lower taxes. It's a short trip for getting anywhere in Simpsonville & Greenville from the IMAX theatre, Woodruff Rd or to GSP airport.

body:

Welcome to this very popular 3 bedroom 2 bath floor plan with optional large bonus area and full bath upstairs. Champions Village is located on South Carolinas only TPC Golf Course in the heart of Prince Creek which is conveniently located near grocery stores, restaurants, shops, golf courses, beaches and marina. Pool and clubhouse on site! Natural Gas Community! With low HOA dues, custom quality homes and a superb location makes Champions Village a very desirable place to call home. *Please Note Front and rear elevation and interior pictures are of similar house built in Champions Village. title: 80 Saresden Cove
body: Nestled in the heart of Sumter, this all brick community boasts many unique features from other new construction neighborhoods across the county. With only eight homes and an appealing cul-de-sac, this area offers the security of a neighborhood without the business of larger developments. Situated just off of the Second Mill Pond, each home has a beautiful view of the water. Enjoy a picnic or go fishing from the community common area that allows access to the pond. Mirroring the neighborhood's distinctiveness, the Watercolor floorplan boasts many alluring features. These 2,000+ sqft homes have 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bath. Also includes a detached two car garage, formal dining room, luxurious kitchen with huge island, stainless steel appliances, and much more. Open to the family room this home is perfect for entertaining or having quality family time. The spacious master bedroom is conveniently located downstairs as well as a guest suite. Make your way upstairs to find two large bedrooms with walk in closets and a full bath. Minutes from either side of town and in the most desirable school zone, this location is one that you cannot beat. Don't miss your chance to own one of our energy efficient smart homes in Saresden. **ONLY TWO HOMES LEFT.**
